webpackJsonp([0xc7be724a89a8],{602:function(e,n){e.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{excerpt:"1. Demonstrate what you've done Lead a team of 5 designers/engineers Delivered a software to WuLiHao to digitize all of their business workflow. Including a customer facing mobile app a driver facing mobile app an admin facing desktop app Made aâ€¦",html:"<h2>1. Demonstrate what you've done</h2>\n<h4>Lead a team of 5 designers/engineers</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Delivered a software to WuLiHao to digitize all of their business workflow.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Including a customer facing mobile app</li>\n<li>a driver facing mobile app</li>\n<li>an admin facing desktop app</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Made a browser</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Detailed draft of functionality</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Capstone</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>2. Ask me a smart question</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>could you tell me more about how TradeGecko has been growing since its\ninception, and what are some of the biggest challenges and milestones\nTradeGecko has faced and overcame?</li>\n<li>What do you think your role as co-founder is now that TradeGecko has grown\ninto a larger firm and how will you continue to deliver value to the\norganization.</li>\n<li>\n<p>Could you discuss TradeGecko's key marketing and customer segmentation\nstrategy?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>and how closely tied is TradeGecko's success to some of its integration\npartners.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>3. Know about the company</h2>\n<p><code>Business</code></p>\n<p>Tons of positive reviews but a fair bit more haters than all of its competitors\ncombined. But most of the hate comes from synchronization issues, and customer\nsupport which TradeGecko has worked on solving recently. The product has a great\ndirection and user interface, most of the backend hiccups seem solvable, and\nproduct seems tighter than all of its competitors.</p>\n<p>Most aggressive pricing model as compared to all its competitors, while similar\nin market share, has as much as 4~6x more revenue generated.</p>\n<p><code>Tiered pricing model</code></p>\n<p>6k CB Rank</p>\n<p>2012 founded</p>\n<p>2015 Series A</p>\n<p>2018 Series B</p>\n<p>Small business - $199/month</p>\n<p>Business - $459/month</p>\n<p>Premium - $799/month</p>\n<p><code>Competitors</code></p>\n<p>Unleashed $85/month 11k CB Rank</p>\n<p>Orderhive $50~150/month</p>\n<p>Dear Systems 114k CB Rank</p>\n<p><code>Feature Summary</code></p>\n<p>Inventory and order management</p>\n<p>online wholesale</p>\n<p>real-time analytics and reporting</p>\n<p>integrates with sales channels (Shopify, Amazon)</p>\n<p>integrates with accounting (Xero, Quickbooks)</p>\n<p>TradeGecko Payments (pay online)</p>\n<p><code>Strengths</code></p>\n<p>UI/UX</p>\n<p>well integrated</p>\n<p>marketing direction</p>\n<p><code>Weaknesses</code></p>\n<p>issues with integrations, sales go missing between TG and Xero</p>\n<p>Problems with reporting by warehouse, years</p>\n<h2>questions for TG</h2>\n<p><code>business</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>why grow so slow, why suddenly pick up traction</li>\n<li>tell me ur numbers (profit, rev, over last x years)</li>\n<li>why did you start this company</li>\n<li>what do you look out for in hires</li>\n<li>why have you chosen to structure the company in this way</li>\n<li>why so ex compared to others</li>\n<li>why target small guys</li>\n<li>what makes them different compared to like unleashed</li>\n<li>what direction is the company taking</li>\n<li>how fast do you envision the company growing? <code>development</code></li>\n<li>monolithic architecture</li>\n<li>*</li>\n</ul>\n<p><code>opportunities</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Negotiate more responsibilities</li>\n<li>Climbing up the ladder</li>\n<li>Assuming more responsibilities</li>\n<li>Roles after senior software dev</li>\n<li>What are the skills that TG can provide me with <code>culture</code></li>\n<li>The mixed reviews on glassdoor</li>\n<li>poor customer service?</li>\n<li>*</li>\n</ul>\n<p><code>compensation</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>equity negotiation</li>\n<li>salary</li>\n<li>year end bonus</li>\n</ul>",frontmatter:{date:"January 15, 2018",path:"tradeGecko",title:"TradeGecko"}}},pathContext:{id:"tradeGecko"}}}});
